<item>
            <title>[LU-6480] leak cmid in kiblnd_dev_need_failover</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6480</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;cmid created by kiblnd_dev_need_failover should always be destroyed, however it is not the case in current implementation so we will leak a cmid on each time call of this function. Fortunately this leak can only happen when dev_failover is enabled. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
